communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Illinois Freedom of Information Act., I hereby request the following records:

Any and all emails, notes and reports being sent and received in regards to the shooting that occurred on 22 July 22 referenced under JF397075

Any and all emails, notes and reports going in and out in regards to the shooting that occurred on 22 July 22 referenced under JF326913

Any and all emails, notes and reports  going in and out in regards to the shooting that occurred on 22 July 22 referenced under JF326932

Any and all emails, notes and reports in regards to the shooting that occurred on 22 July 22 referenced under log # 2022 - 0003147

Any and all emails that reference the Pilsen shooting from July 2022 until October 2024.

Any and all emails that reference Reynoso  from July 2022 until October 2024.
 
Any and all emails from the Cook County States attorney office notifying Chicago Police Department members being charged from January of 2020 to October of 2024.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 5 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

J publi
